you. :-)

By the way, guys, I've emailed Logo and talked to her. She has very 
little time online, and not enough for a big RPG like NBW. She'll be 
back as soon as she can, though.


::Scrap::

Scrap nods. "Wow, you got it pretty rough. Well, we'll be back at 
base as soon as we can get there. Supernova, can we have an energon 
cube back here?"

A panel slides aside, edjecting two energon cubes, one at Scrap and 
one at Bonzai-Tron.

"When we get back to base, Scrap," Supernova's voice sounds inside 
the cockpit, "I get to beat that energon out of you for 
reembursement."
